text: SLHS may refer to: *Seven Lakes High School, a high school located in Katy, Texas. *Standley Lake High School, a high school located in Westminster, Colorado. *San Leandro High School, a high school located in San Leandro, California. *Shilin High School of Commerce, a high school located in Taipei, Taiwan. *Show Low High School, a high school located in Show Low, Arizona *Spanaway Lake High School, a high school located in Spanaway, Washington *South Lakes High School, a high school located in Reston, Virginia. *South Lyon High School, a high school located in South Lyon, Michigan.
